blog.name: alexandro-lima
blog.title: Alexandro Lima - Ilustrador
blog.description: Olá, bem vindo ao meu blog! Sou um ilustrador/arte finalista publicitário com larga experiência de mercado. Considero como seus “mestres inspiradores” Will Eisner, Jack Kirby, John Buscema e Canini. Sou um apreciador de quadrinhos, utilizo muito desta que é considerada a nona arte como fonte de referência para muitos de seus trabalhos.Mesclo trabalho à mão com vetorização e colorização digital em meus trabalhos. Realizo ilustrações, caricaturas, logotipos e pinturas. Este blog tem o objetivo de mostrar o que mais atual ando produzindo. Divulgue e opine!

summary: Do you think Tony regrets not Hugging Peter more ?
body:
Do you think Tony regrets not Hugging Peter more ?

When they’re in the car and he opened the door for him.

And it’s Peter so that has to of happened a few more times.

But as Tony is cradling Peter in his arms… hugging him as he cry’s. Do you think Tony wished he hugged the boy he saw as a son more ?

Tony’s home life was shit.

And Peters parents are dead. Sure he has aunt may but it’s not the same.

Then he got Tony, and he adored every little praise.

So i think he regrets not hugging his son. More then the time he had to watch him die.

Tony & Pepper | Home

 I have a lot of emotions about them after watching the Endgame trailer. These two felt alone and found a...
caption:
Tony & Pepper | Home

I have a lot of emotions about them after watching the Endgame trailer. These two felt alone and found a home in each other. And no matter what happens or what separates them, they always eventually find their way back to each other. Here’s hoping Endgame ends the same way.
